MASKING SCRIPTS
- run with pyana
pyana xtc25410/*r0067*xtc -c myana_avg.cfg -v -n 1000
pyana xtc25410/*r0068*xtc -c myana_cspad.cfg -v -n 2000

- run on written HDF5 files from cheetah
maskRaw.py
maskHit.py
maskType.py

- automatic masking
maskVariance.py
maskNonbondedPixels.py
maskGain.py
maskBorders.py
increaseAutoMask.py

- helper scripts to modify masks
mergeMasks.py
invertMask.py

- view cheetah output with/without applied mask
viewMaskedRaw.py
viewMaskedHit.py
